<html i18n:domain="opencore" metal:use-macro="here/@@standard_macros/master">
  <head>
    <title metal:fill-slot="title" tal:content="string:Invite - ${view/area/Title}" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div metal:fill-slot="content" tal:define="remind request/remind | nothing">
    
    <div class="oc-headingBlock">
      <h1 tal:condition="remind">Remind users</h1>
      <h1 tal:condition="not: remind">Invite users</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div id="oc-content-main">
        <p class="oc-headingContext" tal:condition="remind">Send an email to remind people to join</p>

        <p class="oc-headingContext" tal:condition="not: remind">Send an email to invite people to join</p>
        <form id="oc-inviteByEmail" name="oc-inviteByEmail"
              tal:attributes="action view/request/ACTUAL_URL"
              method="POST">
        <div class="oc-headingBlock">
          <label for="email-invites">To:</label>
          <p class="oc-discreetText" tal:condition="not: remind">Comma separated, or one-per-line</p>
        </div>

          <textarea style="width: 90%;" rows="2" cols="20" id="email-invites" name="email-invites"
                    tal:content="request/form/email-invites | nothing" 
										tal:attributes="readonly remind" />


					<label for="subject">Subject:</label>
          <input tal:condition="remind" type="text" name="subject" tal:attributes='value string:Reminder: Invitation to join "${view/area/Title}" on ${view/portal_title}'><br>
          <input tal:condition="not: remind" type="text" name="subject" tal:attributes='value string:Invitation to join "${view/area/Title}" on ${view/portal_title}'><br>

					<label for="from">From:</label> "<span tal:replace="python: view.loggedinmember.getFullname() or view.loggedinmember.id" />" &lt;<span tal:replace="python: view.loggedinmember.email" />&gt;<br/>

					<label for="message">Message:</label>

<!-- default message for reminder -->
          <textarea tal:condition="remind" rows="20" cols="70"  name="message" i18n:translate="email_remind_default_body">
This is a reminder.

<span i18n:name="inviter_name" tal:replace="python: view.loggedinmember.getFullname() or view.loggedinmember.id" /> has invited you to join "<span i18n:name="project_title" tal:replace="view/area/Title" />" on <span i18n:name="portal_title" tal:replace="view/portal_title" />.
 
<span i18n:name="portal_title" tal:replace="view/portal_title" /> is a free toolset for social change. With <span i18n:name="portal_title" tal:replace="view/portal_title" />, you can build collaborative 
pages for organizing projects. You can also blog, set up mailing lists, store and share files, 
and keep track of tasks.
 
</textarea><br>

<!-- default message for invite -->
          <textarea tal:condition="not: remind" rows="10" cols="70"  name="message" i18n:translate="email_invite_default_body">
<span i18n:name="inviter_name" tal:replace="python: view.loggedinmember.getFullname() or view.loggedinmember.id" /> has invited you to join "<span i18n:name="project_title" tal:replace="view/area/Title" />" on <span i18n:name="portal_title" tal:replace="view/portal_title" />.
 
<span i18n:name="portal_title" tal:replace="view/portal_title" /> is a free toolset for social change. With <span i18n:name="portal_title" tal:replace="view/portal_title" />, you can build collaborative 
pages for organizing projects. You can also blog, set up mailing lists, store and share files, 
and keep track of tasks.
 
</textarea><br>

This will be added to all messages:
<div style="background-color: #ddddff;">
<pre i18n:translate="email_invite_static_body">
<span i18n:name="user_message"></span>
To accept this invitation or learn more about the project, click here: 
<span i18n:name="project_title">${join_url}</span>.


---------------------------------------------------------------------
This message was sent from <span i18n:name="portal_title"
tal:replace="view/portal_title" />.  
To contact <span i18n:name="portal_title" tal:replace="view/portal_title" />, go here:
<span i18n:name="site_contact_url" tal:replace="string: ${view/portal/absolute_url}/contact-site-admin" />
</pre> </div>


          <input tal:condition="remind" type="submit" 
                 name="task|remind-email-invites" value="Send"
                 class="oc-button" />

          <input tal:condition="not: remind" type="submit" 
                 name="task|email-invites" value="Send"
                 class="oc-button" />
        </form>

      </div>
          
    </div><!-- end content-fill-slot -->
  </body>
</html>
